{"tid":2048634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡貿工部長陳振聲：沒有那麼多綿羊去生產棉花","createTime":"2020-06-03T02:45:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T03:29:15.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b1d4cbb5eaf258190153d28521230ef7d7bd2ca5","tid":2048634,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T02:45:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.Xq6MR8paMf.pm0xWiHjvQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQyNi42NjY2NjY2NjY2NjY3/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/Nfz_LecFImAvxAeHPfqt8g--~B/aD00MDA7dz02MDA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-06/fe82c490-a524-11ea-bbfa-e2835fd78425\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F.Xq6MR8paMf.pm0xWiHjvQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQyNi42NjY2NjY2NjY2NjY3%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FNfz_LecFImAvxAeHPfqt8g--~B%2FaD00MDA7dz02MDA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-06%2Ffe82c490-a524-11ea-bbfa-e2835fd78425&h=03def1f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新加坡貿易與工業部長陳振聲日前接受當地傳媒訪問時便「開口夾着脷」，他在解釋為何新加坡要依賴國際貿易、不能在本地設置生產線時，就以口罩為例，說新加坡沒有那麼多綿羊去生產棉花。一番「棉花出自（綿）羊身上」的偉論旋即成為網民熱話，陳部長事後亦在社交平台承認口誤，還打趣說要好好補眠。<br />\n<br />\n他辯稱自己當時是「不小心、說話說太快」，事後回看都覺好笑，又強調「棉花絕對不是來自綿羊，而是植物！這幾個禮拜一直在想口罩原料的替代品，但可惜的是，新加坡既沒有綿羊也沒有棉花。」<br />\n<br />\n今次已非陳振聲首次失言，在新冠肺炎疫情爆發初期，各地人民到超市搶購物資，他曾揶揄港人瘋搶口罩、廁紙的行為太「低能」、「Monkey See, Monkey Do」，呼籲新加坡人不要仿效，更語出驚人：「無廁紙，用水就可以，為何我們會做那麼低能的事情呢？我真是受不了。」其後星洲疫情惡化，當地也出現同樣「低能」情況，民眾爭相到超市搶購各類防疫用品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/中環解密-稱棉花產自綿羊-星貿工部長陳振聲認衰-193300973.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0%E8%A7%A3%E5%AF%86-%E7%A8%B1%E6%A3%89%E8%8A%B1%E7%94%A2%E8%87%AA%E7%B6%BF%E7%BE%8A-%E6%98%9F%E8%B2%BF%E5%B7%A5%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7%E9%99%B3%E6%8C%AF%E8%81%B2%E8%AA%8D%E8%A1%B0-193300973.html&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgYCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=7b67acf7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/中環解密-稱棉花產自綿羊-星貿工部長陳振聲認衰-193300973.html</a>"},{"pid":"07d6d7a73c57bc1a90849b86a9f4cbaf9f9932a5","tid":2048634,"uid":11291,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T02:47:27.000Z","msg":"又係呢條傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9844956539253b59770c67f9e09e43117dd0f61c","tid":2048634,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T03:26:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d883e4494ceb07621ca67d9a8effa79ffa7daa6","tid":2048634,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T03:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />弱智猴子"},{"pid":"2acba32e13561a13671b500606f9b666ee6327cc","tid":2048634,"uid":23087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T03:29:15.000Z","msg":"垃圾坡狗"}]}